Internal use function.

This function's parameters and processing may change in future SDKs.

Handler for interrupt line 4 on 78XX. These are directly tied to the CIU3. This func is used only upon initializtion - to silently clear all pending interrupts.

Internal use function.

Handler for interrupt lines 2 and 3. These are directly tied to the CIU. The handler queries the status of the CIU and calls the secondary handler for the CIU interrupt that occurred.

Internal use function.

This function's parameters and processing may change in future SDKs.

Handler for interrupt line 3, the DPI_DMA will have different value per core, all other fields values are identical for different cores. These are directly tied to the CIU. The handler queries the status of the CIU and calls the secondary handler for the CIU interrupt that occurred.
